  },
  "ctaBand": {
    "eyebrow": "Start with your real file",
    "heading": "We'll set up the features your books actually need.",
    "lede": "Get a free QuickBooks file review or book a discovery call. We'll look at how your QBO file is configured against the features your business needs, and show you exactly where setup or cleanup will help. No pitch. Independent firm — not Intuit.",
